i\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nseed"},{"pid":"e43611d1d4aa6225a3bdae70c55852f10d64f34f","tid":385714,"uid":74380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T20:02:42.000Z","msg":"你的資訊真有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8068d4a7beafaab4f9e5cb3fc1a7b7a9ef0612d","tid":385714,"uid":123524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T20:23:53.000Z","msg":"又柯柏文又利世民抬橋<br />\n擺明係做騷的世緻女"},{"pid":"ea625f66337a7c4de4c7422d6ffa25b4c68ba50a","tid":385714,"uid":69886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T20:31:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又柯柏文又利世民抬橋<br />\n擺明係做騷的世緻女</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/spqS8kS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FspqS8kS.jpg&h=96f55abc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e24baadec74030f633d7e460d3aff29cc5ba250e","tid":385714,"uid":5137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T20:49:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同香港人玩就亞氏保加<br />\n同鬼佬玩又船P又劈酒<br />\n死港女</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">18歲少女棄大學做程式員：「<span style=\"color: red;\">鬼佬</span>IT 人唔係毒撚！」</span><br />\n<br />\n香港IT人係毒撚！</blockquote><br />\n確實唔係毒撚 係狗姐<br />\nIt is a dog"},{"pid":"eacd999ea300a3e91bd5b2ec2f5e3c512b8e9283","tid":385714,"uid":123524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T23:09:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又柯柏文又利世民抬橋<br />\n擺明係做騷的世緻女</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/spqS8kS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FspqS8kS.jpg&h=96f55abc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n離開屋企<br />\n<br />\n考完試，升中六，Clara 付諸行動，整個學期幾乎無返學，埋頭研究寫程式。<br />\n<br />\n學校通知屋企，父母當然反對，要捉她返學。<br />\n<br />\nClara 毅然離家出走。<br />\n<br />\n由於學校在調景嶺區，機緣巧合認識了孫柏文 &mdash; 當時的區議員助理。<br />\n<br />\n「之前就識佢。離家出走後冇晒錢，唔知點好，就去揾佢。」<br />\n<br />\n孫柏文是智庫獅子山學會的創辦人，同時是財演、馬主，身份多，人脈廣，別看他平日瘋癲，想不到觀察力頗強，他跟 Clara 談了幾句，就已看出了她可能是 Asperger（亞氏保加症），還直接問了她。<br />\n<br />\n「當時嚇了一跳，我的確係有啲。」<br />\n<br />\n孫柏文介紹Clara到智庫做暑期工，擴闊她的生活圈子。兩人年紀相差廿幾年，關係亦師亦友，對她影響頗大。<br />\n<br />\n後來，Clara終於找到一分長工，為該公司開發了一個社交媒體分析系統，算是她的第一個「Baby」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://startupbeat.hkej.com/?p=45673\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstartupbeat.hkej.com%2F%3Fp%3D45673&d=dfRZWSKrOdZ8x2zAo%2BZPdv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=402efa4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://startupbeat.hkej.com/?p=45673</a>"},{"pid":"ee05240afd99e3887a1b808b535d5e4131b35e72","tid":385714,"uid":47378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T23:14:13.000Z","msg":"CS 同programmer 完全冇衝突好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0735b613bd87a66e091c4f4fd293870f3e6c8440","tid":385714,"uid":48947,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T23:19:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同香港人玩就亞氏保加<br />\n同鬼佬玩又船P又劈酒<br />\n死港女</blockquote><br />\n我都正想講<br />\n又係依條臭閪<br />\n之前又話唔識同人相處有亞氏保加<br />\n依家就去完船p<br />\n依條八婆假撚到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba10c50c2916323de307bee13a35b4967c6aeece","tid":385714,"uid":93588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T00:54:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">她獲介紹到一家公關公司研究開發一個社交媒體監察程式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"5125e069d0f517a93d5ee0292f06d405d0f9d57c","tid":385714,"uid":59747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T00:56:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「IT 人唔係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n這份程式開發員的工作改變了 Clara 對世界的看法，她指公司同事及老闆都很開明，終於找到不再被人標籤的地方。而家人見她的工作穩定，開始逐漸認同她，關係沒有先前緊張。最重要的是，憑著共同興趣，她結識了一班志同道合的朋友，她亦努力克服自己的症狀，學習與人建立關係。<br />\n<br />\n只是，社會上不少人對於從事 IT 的人好像都有一種偏見，不是說他們是「IT 狗」，就是「毒 L」，記者問她會否擔心會再被標籤？Clara 斬釘截鐵地說，「IT 人唔係毒 L<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。『Geek』係一種心態，我地不斷埋頭苦幹鑽研我地喜愛嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，只係外人唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/highres_463216242-1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2Fhighres_463216242-1.jpeg&h=1646054b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲ 找到志同道合的朋友，有話題自然更容易相處吧。（圖片由受訪者提供）</span><br />\n<br />\n有片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/unwirehk/videos/10154906285964103/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Funwirehk%2Fvideos%2F10154906285964103%2F&d=dfRZWSKrOdZ8x2zAo%2BZPdv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=a06faf1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/unwirehk/videos/10154906285964103/</a></div></blockquote><br />\n屌，咪又係洋腸港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301a6c350bda362074793156c8e7cd99e4b4e20e","tid":385714,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T01:05:06.000Z","msg":"亞氏保加閪"},{"pid":"858fa6e0b9830415673cdc44ec47606b370457ac","tid":385714,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T01:06:12.000Z","msg":"又回帶binc"},{"pid":"87122773f938336ea7ee428d9c5d4528d1220f2b","tid":385714,"uid":24805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T01:14:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢係唔係做IT搞到幾日無飯食？<br />\n張張相都面青口嘴白既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n獅子山學會既人有邊個樣係正常？"},{"pid":"3bd3f7c1db210b5a77599f85bcee49ae98ba8edc","tid":385714,"uid":52062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T01:20:04.000Z","msg":"其實兩樣野無衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}